al/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e13180ecd56d0d1f72bfd7deb0df3bb41350a0","tid":480272,"uid":97309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"喂近排睇viutv廣告賣有間野叫好師傅嘅平台介紹裝修師傅, 成個trivago咁, 唔知得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059b9253eb38d8630aa0ffc2b6843ace8474de6a","tid":480272,"uid":10637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>勸你搵親屬 或者好熟嘅朋友嘅親屬<br />\n<br />\n裝修呢 d 野 遇人不淑會煩到你想跳樓<br />\n要搵就一定要搵 d 好信得過 成日有機會見到嘅人<br />\n<br />\n住何情況下都一定要簽合約 合約愈詳細愈好<br />\n<br />\n完工日期要寫明 <br />\n工錢 材料要寫低 分幾多期 每期俾幾多<br />\n數目要寫得清清楚楚<br />\n傾過包乜野全部要落合約<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾人抛兩抛就算 唔肯寫清楚就唔好搵佢</blockquote><br />\n呢個真</blockquote><br />\n明白，最緊要講包咩就寫入合約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n親戚有d先食得深<br />\n唔識又扮識<br />\nDiu又唔係"},{"pid":"469f593114d6025872a37cf6c7f10903446de026","tid":480272,"uid":17832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"516106add57cbbdda181a635745fc0013c9a14cd","tid":480272,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但親屬有時都奶野 除時反目成仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要張報價單，細節<br />\n價可以blur 再問下熟人之類<br />\n依家冇得屈 最緊要識報海關 商品條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁梗係自己諗清楚個 &quot;親戚&quot; 係咩人啦<br />\n唔通一年見一次個 d 親戚咩 <br />\n講成日見知咩料個 d<br />\n<br />\n自己識諗啦"},{"pid":"6fdc61ad03a7b145cf4602a7fc329b2ce52e9745","tid":480272,"uid":38738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"小弟做裝修，有意就留個contact交流下"},{"pid":"693d0160c8e37c38dea813b913fff4f658b8193a","tid":480272,"uid":7961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"搵熟人的確隨時唔熟唔食....<br />\n但咁多位巴打有無用過邊間公司推介<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發現叫人裝修真係慘...<br />\n有一間fb睇到好靚...<br />\n上門睇完，之黎一直話等等等...<br />\n等足一個月先話唔得閒做<br />\n<br />\n另外兩間直頭唔覆機<br />\n<br />\n裝修真係好似唔憂做咁，求人準許我俾錢佢駛咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1574e46ce002bc8f2a1b42306f3ca17f851520b","tid":480272,"uid":53325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂近排睇viutv廣告賣有間野叫好師傅嘅平台介紹裝修師傅, 成個trivago咁, 唔知得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前在FB見到佢d廣告，見佢d完工相都幾靚就搵左佢地報價<br />\n見張報價單都列得幾詳細，所以就用咗  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d72d4cdfc8beebd5ceec343195a52ad22710d66","tid":480272,"uid":75466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"其實香港點解冇裝修大集團<br />\n比較有信譽 公信力"},{"pid":"8a22444198986594bd52c4025b5ff25e8cda8aca","tid":480272,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港點解冇裝修大集團<br />\n比較有信譽 公信力</blockquote><br />\n好似都有但貴到飛起"},{"pid":"f4b1ff019a73b6c5e5ee97be308ea1fddfea269d","tid":480272,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喂近排睇viutv廣告賣有間野叫好師傅嘅平台介紹裝修師傅, 成個trivago咁, 唔知得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前在FB見到佢d廣告，見佢d完工相都幾靚就搵左佢地報價<br />\n見張報價單都列得幾詳細，所以就用咗  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgm